rows.label: qst700803_msg0001
rows.name:
Phew, finally done collecting...
There can't be any more, right?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0002
rows.name: ...Huh? This presence... who's there!?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0003
rows.name:
Fuffuffu... Yare yare, looks
like we've been found, mo.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0004
rows.name:
This trash... Could it
be that you did this?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0005
rows.name:
That's right, mo. To collect all
the traps Ryuuryuu and the others
set, you guys are pretty good, mo.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0006
rows.name:
However! Now that you stand before
us four brothers, you have a 10,000%
chance of not winning, mo!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0007
rows.name: Four brothers... Who are you?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0008
rows.name:
Fuffuffu... Clean out your
ears and listen well, mo!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0009
rows.name: Ryuuryuu!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0010
rows.name: Kachocho!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0011
rows.name: Yokuyoku!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0012
rows.name: Komeme!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0013
rows.name: Though born at different times!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0014
rows.name: We swear to die at the same!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0015
rows.name: The four brothers who answer to no one!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0016
rows.name: Our name is...!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0017
rows.name: "The Four Rampaging Angels of Iira"!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0018
rows.name:
"The Three Strongest
Nopon Warlords +1"!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0019
rows.name: "Yokuyoku and His Merry Friends"!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0020
rows.name: Mo!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0021
rows.name: ...None of those match.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0022
rows.name:
Mo! We decided to go with
"The Three Strongest Nopon
Warlords +1" last time, mo!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0023
rows.name:
The "+1" sounds so bad, mo! Let's
just stick with "The Four Rampaging
Angels of Iira," mo!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0024
rows.name:
Momomo! I hate such a lame
name, mo! Let's go with "Yokuyoku
and His Merry Friends"...

rows.label: qst700803_msg0025
rows.name:
Okay, okay! Whether you're four
brothers or merry friends, can
you let me talk for a bit?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0026
rows.name: Momo?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0027
rows.name: Why are you all dumping trash here?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0028
rows.name:
You see, a certain old woman looks
forward to coming here for a walk.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0029
rows.name: So, could you please stop doing this?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0030
rows.name:
Mo? Did that old lady say
she was troubled, mo?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0031
rows.name: Eh? Do you know that old woman?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0032
rows.name: ...We're sorry, mo.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0033
rows.name: ...We won't do it again, mo.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0034
rows.name: Ah, yes. As long as you understand.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0035
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Huh? They're surprisingly obedient.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0036
rows.name: ...Is what...

rows.label: qst700803_msg0037
rows.name: you thought we'd say, mo!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0038
rows.name: Everyone! Let's split up and run, mo!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0039
rows.name: As expected of our eldest brother, mo!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0040
rows.name: To run is to win, mo!

rows.label: qst700803_msg0042
rows.name: They got away!?

rows.label: qst700803_msg0043
rows.name:
Well, it's all right if we
couldn't catch them here.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0044
rows.name: We know who the culprits are.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0045
rows.name:
If we secure them one by one,
there should be no problem.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0046
rows.name:
It seems they all fled
into the capital.

rows.label: qst700803_msg0047
rows.name:
All right! Then, let's find them
one by one and report to Oulu-san!
